other women since the two split up five months ago.
   ``We're going to go get down to the Tyson-Givens game, are we?''
Downey said, referring to the prominent disputes between heavyweight
champion Mike Tyson and his wife, Robin Givens. ``Well, I'm good at
it.''
   The couple had no children. Downey has three daughters from
previous marriages.
